---
import Base from "@/layouts/Base.astro";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
---

<Base
  title="Swag"
  meta_title="Sovereign Engineering Swag"
  description="Get your Sovereign Engineering merchandise - shirts, hoodies, and more"
  showCallToAction={false}
>
  <!-- Hero Section with Black Hat Image -->
  <header class="relative h-[420px] w-full overflow-hidden bg-black flex items-center justify-center">
    <img
      src="/images/swag/black-hat.png"
      alt="Sovereign Engineering Black Hat Design"
      class="w-3/4 h-auto object-contain opacity-80"
    />
  </header>

  <!-- Products Section -->
  <section class="w-full text-white bg-black py-8 sm:py-16">
    <div class="container max-w-[960px] mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-4xl mb-8 pt-8 text-center text-white font-normal">The Story of Our Swag</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Each piece tells a story of sovereign engineering - from the tools we build to the principles we uphold
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- SEC-02 Hat Section -->
      <div class="mb-24">
        <div class="text-center mb-12">
          <h3 class="text-3xl mb-6 font-normal">SEC-02: The Original</h3>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
            The hat that started it all - representing the foundational principles of sovereign engineering
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center gap-12">
          <div class="lg:w-1/2">
            <div class="bg-transparent">
              <img
                src="/images/swag/SEC02_Hat.png"
                alt="SEC-02 Hat"
                class="w-full h-auto rounded-lg shadow-xl bg-transparent"
              />
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="lg:w-1/2">
            <h4 class="text-2xl mb-6 font-normal">The Original Design</h4>
            <div class="space-y-4 text-lg text-gray-300">
              <p>
                The SEC-02 hat represents the original vision of sovereign engineering - a commitment to building tools that empower individuals and communities to take control of their digital lives.
              </p>
              <p>
                This design embodies the spirit of the early days when the principles of digital sovereignty were first being forged. It serves as a reminder of where we started and the foundational values that continue to guide our work.
              </p>
              <p>
                Wearing this hat is a statement of allegiance to the core mission: creating technology that serves people, not corporations, and building systems that enable true digital autonomy.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- SEC03 Shirt - Left -->
      <div class="mb-24">
        <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center gap-12">
          <div class="lg:w-1/2">
            <!-- Main large image display -->
            <div class="bg-transparent mb-6">
              <img
                id="sec03-main"
                src="/images/swag/SEC03_Back.png"
                alt="SEC03 Shirt Back"
                class="w-full h-auto rounded-lg shadow-xl bg-transparent transition-all duration-300"
              />
            </div>
            <!-- Thumbnail navigation -->
            <div class="flex gap-4">
              <div class="bg-transparent cursor-pointer group">
                <img
                  src="/images/swag/SEC03_Front.png"
                  alt="SEC03 Shirt Front"
                  class="w-24 h-auto rounded-lg shadow-lg bg-transparent transition-all duration-200 group-hover:shadow-xl group-hover:scale-105"
                  onclick="changeMainImage('sec03-main', '/images/swag/SEC03_Front.png', 'SEC03 Shirt Front')"
                />
              </div>
              <div class="bg-transparent cursor-pointer group">
                <img
                  src="/images/swag/SEC03_Back.png"
                  alt="SEC03 Shirt Back"
                  class="w-24 h-auto rounded-lg shadow-lg bg-transparent transition-all duration-200 group-hover:shadow-xl group-hover:scale-105"
                  onclick="changeMainImage('sec03-main', '/images/swag/SEC03_Back.png', 'SEC03 Shirt Back')"
                />
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="lg:w-1/2">
            <h3 class="text-3xl mb-6 mt-12 first:mt-0 font-normal">SEC-03: Ecash</h3>
            <div class="space-y-4 text-lg text-gray-300">
              <p>
                The SEC03 collection represents the foundational principles of sovereign engineering. The front design features a stylized building engulfed in flames, symbolizing the destruction of old systems and the birth of new ones.
              </p>
              <p>
                On the back, you'll find our core mantra: "Build the tools. Ship the future." This phrase encapsulates our mission to create the infrastructure that enables true digital sovereignty.
              </p>
              <p>
                The red and black color scheme represents the intensity of our commitment to breaking free from centralized control and building systems that serve individuals, not corporations.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- SEC04 Shirt - Right -->
      <div class="mb-24">
        <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row-reverse items-center gap-12">
          <div class="lg:w-1/2">
            <!-- Main large image display -->
            <div class="bg-transparent mb-6">
              <img
                id="sec04-main"
                src="/images/swag/SEC04_Back.png"
                alt="SEC04 Shirt Back"
                class="w-full h-auto rounded-lg shadow-xl bg-transparent transition-all duration-300"
              />
            </div>
            <!-- Thumbnail navigation -->
            <div class="flex gap-4">
              <div class="bg-transparent cursor-pointer group">
                <img
                  src="/images/swag/SEC04_Front.png"
                  alt="SEC04 Shirt Front"
                  class="w-24 h-auto rounded-lg shadow-lg bg-transparent transition-all duration-200 group-hover:shadow-xl group-hover:scale-105"
                  onclick="changeMainImage('sec04-main', '/images/swag/SEC04_Front.png', 'SEC04 Shirt Front')"
                />
              </div>
              <div class="bg-transparent cursor-pointer group">
                <img
                  src="/images/swag/SEC04_Back.png"
                  alt="SEC04 Shirt Back"
                  class="w-24 h-auto rounded-lg shadow-lg bg-transparent transition-all duration-200 group-hover:shadow-xl group-hover:scale-105"
                  onclick="changeMainImage('sec04-main', '/images/swag/SEC04_Back.png', 'SEC04 Shirt Back')"
                />
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="lg:w-1/2">
            <h3 class="text-3xl mb-6 mt-12 first:mt-0 font-normal">SEC-04: Trilemmas</h3>
            <div class="space-y-4 text-lg text-gray-300">
              <p>
                The SEC04 design features a compass rose, representing our commitment to navigating the complex landscape of digital sovereignty. The intricate red pattern on black symbolizes the precision and care required in our work.
              </p>
              <p>
                The back design incorporates elements that guide us: the stars of navigation, the tools of our trade, and the principles that keep us oriented toward true north - individual autonomy and technological freedom.
              </p>
              <p>
                This piece embodies the spirit of exploration and discovery that drives sovereign engineering forward, always seeking new ways to empower individuals through technology.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- SEC05 Shirt - Left -->
      <div class="mb-24">
        <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center gap-12">
          <div class="lg:w-1/2">
            <!-- Main large image display -->
            <div class="bg-transparent mb-6">
              <img
                id="sec05-main"
                src="/images/swag/SEC05_Back.png"
                alt="SEC05 Shirt Back"
                class="w-full h-auto rounded-lg shadow-xl bg-transparent transition-all duration-300"
              />
            </div>
            <!-- Thumbnail navigation -->
            <div class="flex gap-4">
              <div class="bg-transparent cursor-pointer group">
                <img
                  src="/images/swag/SEC05_Front.png"
                  alt="SEC05 Shirt Front"
                  class="w-24 h-auto rounded-lg shadow-lg bg-transparent transition-all duration-200 group-hover:shadow-xl group-hover:scale-105"
                  onclick="changeMainImage('sec05-main', '/images/swag/SEC05_Front.png', 'SEC05 Shirt Front')"
                />
              </div>
              <div class="bg-transparent cursor-pointer group">
                <img
                  src="/images/swag/SEC05_Back.png"
                  alt="SEC05 Shirt Back"
                  class="w-24 h-auto rounded-lg shadow-lg bg-transparent transition-all duration-200 group-hover:shadow-xl group-hover:scale-105"
                  onclick="changeMainImage('sec05-main', '/images/swag/SEC05_Back.png', 'SEC05 Shirt Back')"
                />
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="lg:w-1/2">
            <h3 class="text-3xl mb-6 mt-12 first:mt-0 font-normal">SEC-05: YOLO Mode</h3>
            <div class="space-y-4 text-lg text-gray-300">
              <p>
                The SEC05 collection represents the future we're building - a world where technology serves humanity, not the other way around. The circuit-like design on the front symbolizes the interconnected systems we create.
              </p>
              <p>
                The back features a more abstract representation of the digital landscape, showing how individual nodes connect to form resilient networks that can't be controlled by any single entity.
              </p>
              <p>
                The green and brown color palette represents growth, sustainability, and the organic nature of truly decentralized systems that evolve and adapt naturally.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Call to Action Section -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-black text-white border-t border-white">
    <div class="container max-w-[960px] mx-auto px-4 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Ready to Get Your Swag?</h2>
      <p class="text-xl mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-gray-300">
        Visit our webshop to browse the full collection and place your order
      </p>
      <a
        href="https://shop.soveng.org"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="inline-block bg-white text-black px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-semibold text-lg hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors duration-200"
      >
        Visit Webshop →
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>



  <script>
    // Function to change main image
    function changeMainImage(elementId: string, imageSrc: string, imageAlt: string) {
      const mainImage = document.getElementById(elementId) as HTMLImageElement;
      if (mainImage) {
        mainImage.src = imageSrc;
        mainImage.alt = imageAlt;
      }
    }
  </script>
</Base> 